<dl id="n51178m"> <dt class="nbunit"><a name="n51" href="#n51178m">N51 (VI.B.44)</a>:  <a href="../../ff/fnbs/n51all.htm#n51178m"> 178(m)</a></dt> <dd> <blockquote> borders</blockquote> <dd class="well"> <blockquote class="sources"><mark>Borders</mark>. &mdash; Lengths of painted canvass six feet Hide hung across the stage to mask the border lights, the top of the scenes, and those not in use. <small> William G. Fay, <a name="WGFS" href="../../ff/fdra/fdex.htm#WGFS"><cite title="source">A Short Glossary of Theatrical Terms</cite></a> (Aug 1930) 00</small></blockquote> </dd></dl>
